OL,3,CHunger striker and Victims Campaigner
OL,4,Cand the football team that united them
OL,6,FA new documentary about a highly
OL,7,Fsuccessful youth football team from
OL,8,Fnorth Belfast, whose members included
OL,9,FVictims Campaigner Raymond McCord and
OL,10,Fhunger striker Bobby Sands, hopes to
OL,11,Fserve as a "cautionary tale" and to
OL,12,Fshow how communities worked and played
OL,13,Ftogether before the Troubles tore
OL,14,Ffriendships apart.
OL,16,FRealt Na Mara - or Star of the Sea -
OL,17,Fhas received an emotional response by
OL,18,Fthose involved, as well as those who
OL,19,Fare unfamiliar with the story of the
OL,20,FBelfast boys who favoured football
OL,21,Fabove all else...
